{"tid":403871,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沈祖堯引錢穆籲勿忘中國　新亞學生會反問：錢所指的「中國」是哪個「中國」","createTime":"2017-09-17T14:07:32.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-18T09:45:54.000Z","uid":53379,"like":134,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"dcc8b9fbd2ca6633ade7b719ae3234a81994ac3b","tid":403871,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:07:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">沈祖堯引錢穆籲勿忘中國　新亞學生會反問：錢所指的「中國」是哪個「中國」？</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20151204/s00001/1449223466750_8B563E8E741C601062E459DDD535966B.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20151204%2Fs00001%2F1449223466750_8B563E8E741C601062E459DDD535966B.jpg&h=2238881a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n中大校長沈祖堯昨發表網誌，稱對有學生在校園觀賽時噓國歌非常痛心，認為無論如何都不應侮辱國歌，又引用新亞書院創辦人錢穆所說「你是中國人，不要忘記中國」。新亞學生會回應沈祖堯指出，對沈引用錢穆的話大惑不解，指錢穆南下香港，「是因為逃避中共的魔爪」，反問沈「錢穆先生所指的『中國』是哪一個『中國』？」<br />\n<br />\n新亞學生會發表《給沈校長的公開信》，指中華人民共和國開國領袖毛澤東曾在《丟掉幻想準備鬥爭》一文中，點名批鬥錢穆，是被「帝國主義及其走狗中國的反動政府」控制的「新式大小知識分子」之一。而錢穆辭去新亞書院校長一職後，遠赴台灣，一生從未踏足對岸。<br />\n<br />\n新亞學生會稱，「敢問校長，錢穆先生所指的『中國』是哪一個『中國』？」公開信中指錢穆是新亞書院創校先賢，有崇高而不可取代的地位，懇請沈正視歷史，不宜引喻失義。下款日期更為「民國一零四年十二月四日」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151204/s00001/1449220772563\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151204%2Fs00001%2F1449220772563&d=7WI26dtcN9nj09nBXiawhnIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=bbb5e52e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20151204%2Fs00001%2F1449220772563&h=fadcca99\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20151204/s00001/1449220772563</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 沈祖堯"},{"pid":"5f3ddef19818d4a4e1599b7292b8c949435b2156","tid":403871,"uid":60787,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:08:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 撚狗"},{"pid":"daaaa2ee18bf31808446d6bad00547f5ba12752f","tid":403871,"uid":82532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:12:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83c4fba2031269989dea1a68c104bcfa9ef75ecf","tid":403871,"uid":63909,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:13:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />真係撚狗咁撚"},{"pid":"d5e0f289c272993300dcb440d69e786a9aa20f66","tid":403871,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:13:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3321073caaf1acca130742330c52ade8915a3025","tid":403871,"uid":1781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:14:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9724693ef95e519f5477f322ea89eeeea484c41","tid":403871,"uid":29461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:16:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"84143c453cd6c9b7cbc7dba0f75f3141e0e9feba","tid":403871,"uid":23707,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-17T14:21:08.000Z","msg":"希望呢d質素keep到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"